title: Fringe radicals can't undermine Australia's love of multiculturalism... (Australian Human Rights Commission)
text: ( Source : Australian Human Rights Commission ) As Australians we typically think of ourselves as relaxed and welcoming people. So it has been sad to see so many police had to be deployed in Bendigo and Parramatta during the past week or so.
